com.thetransactioncompany.cors
Class HeaderFieldName

java.lang.Object
  com.thetransactioncompany.cors.HeaderFieldName

public class HeaderFieldName
extends java.lang.Object

Represents an HTTP header field name. Provides an equals(java.lang.Object) method to compare two header names using case-insensitive matching (RFC 2616, section 4.2).

Header field name examples:

  • Content-Type
  • User-Agent
  • X-Requested-With

Version:
1.3.2 (2010-09-26)
Author:
Vladimir Dzhuvinov
